data.title: Georgia National Guard, Army - Speeches by MG George E. Leach, Chief of NGB, to Service Schools, Chemical Warfare and Field Artillery Courses, 1934, 1939 - 1940
data.text:
From the Series:

This series consists of records of the Georgia Militia and the Georgia National Guard, 1779-1975. Among the records are reports, orders, rosters, correspondence, muster rolls, and pay rolls.
